Right now your Function is just forwarding raw JSON.
If you want to punch into the body (e.g., read eventId, docId, correlationId) before calling the Message API, you can use Jackson.

Here’s a safe snippet that you can drop in MessageRelayFunction before calling MessageApiRelay.send(...).

