Inside run(...) before the MessageApiRelay.send(...):

// Parse JSON body (safe)
ObjectMapper mapper = new ObjectMapper();
String corr = firstNonBlank(correlationId, messageId, invocationId); // default

try {
    JsonNode root = mapper.readTree(body);

    // Example: if JSON has "correlationId"
    if (root.hasNonNull("correlationId")) {
        corr = root.get("correlationId").asText();
    }

    // Example: log eventId/docId if present
    String eventId = root.path("event").path("eventId").asText(null);
    String docId   = root.path("event").path("docId").asText(null);

    log.info("[Relay] Parsed body corr=" + corr
            + " eventId=" + safe(eventId)
            + " docId=" + safe(docId));

} catch (Exception jex) {
    log.warning("[Relay] Failed to parse JSON body: " + jex.getMessage()
            + " | using fallback correlationId=" + corr);
}

Helper:

private static String safe(String s) {
    return (s == null || s.isBlank()) ? "-" : s;
}


